      "content": {
        "text": "INT. NEXUS-7 - DOCKING BAY - CONTINUOUS\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:01:00]\nCAPTAIN ELARA (35, sharp-eyed, no-nonsense explorer) steps out with her team: DR. KAI (42, brilliant but arrogant scientist), TECHIE LENA (28, optimistic gadget whiz), and ROOKIE MARCUS (22, wide-eyed newbie).\n\nELARA\n(adjusting suit comms)\nAlright, team. Scans show life support's holding\u2014barely. We're here for the artifact. In, out, no heroics.\n\nKAI\n(scoffing, checking his scanner)\nHeroics? This station was experimenting with quantum entanglement. If the artifact's real, it could rewrite physics. We're talking doorways to alternate realities.\n\nLENA\n(excited, fiddling with a drone)\nCool! Like, parallel universes where I'm a rock star?\n\nMARCUS\n(nervous)\nOr where we're all dead. Guys, the logs said the crew vanished. Poof.\n\nELARA\nFocus. Kai, lead on the artifact chamber. Lena, get systems online. Marcus, stick with me\u2014watch for anomalies.\n\nThey move through dim corridors, lights humming erratically.\n\nCUT TO:\n",
