      },
      "content": {
        "text": "INT. CORRIDOR ALPHA - MOMENTS LATER\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:03:30]\nEchoes of distant machinery. The team passes holographic logs flickering on walls\u2014ghostly crew members mid-sentence.\n\nHOLO-CREW MEMBER (projection)\n...the entanglement field is stable. But the echoes... they're not ours...\n\nKAI\n(stopping, intrigued)\nEchoes? That's new. The artifact must be creating temporal feedback loops.\n\nLENA\n(activating a panel)\nPower's at 20%. I can reroute from auxiliary\u2014wait, there's a signal. Incoming?\n\nA low HUM builds. The walls shimmer like water.\n\nMARCUS\nUh, Captain? The floor's... vibrating.\n\nSuddenly, a RIPPLE in reality\u2014a shadowy figure appears at the corridor's end, mirroring Elara's stance.\n\nELARA\nWhat the hell?\n\nThe figure vanishes. Alarms blare softly.\n\nKAI\nThat's it! Quantum echo. The artifact's bleeding alternate versions of us into this reality.\n\nLENA\nSo, like doppelgangers? Awesome... or terrifying?\n\nELARA\nTerrifying wins. Move faster.\n\nCUT TO:\n",
