      "content": {
        "text": "INT. CORRIDOR ALPHA - FLEEING\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:18:00]\nThe team runs, dodging merging realities: Walls turn to jelly, gravity flips briefly.\n\nLENA\n(panting)\nThe shuttle's this way! But the station's destabilizing.\n\nMARCUS\nAnd the echoes are following!\n\nBehind: A horde of alternate selves\u2014heroic, villainous, ridiculous\u2014chase them.\n\nECHO-KAI (villainous)\nJoin us! Become infinite!\n\nKAI\nThat's me? I look evil.\n\nELARA\nKeep moving! Lena, can you seal doors?\n\nLENA\n(using gadget)\nOn it\u2014plasma lock!\n\nDoors slam, but echoes phase through.\n\nMARCUS\nThey ghost-mode now?!\n\nA super-crazy echo appears: A giant, mecha-version of the team fused into one robot.\n\nMECHA-ECHO\n(booming)\nWe are Legion! Surrender to the void!\n\nIt fires confetti lasers\u2014harmless but disorienting.\n\nELARA\nThis is insane! Shoot it!\n\nThey fire stun guns\u2014confetti explodes everywhere.\n\nCUT TO:\n",
