      "content": {
        "text": "INT. DOCKING BAY - CLIMAX\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:22:00]\nThey reach the shuttle. The artifact's influence spreads: The gas giant below warps into a smiley face.\n\nKAI\nI can fix this! Reverse the entanglement!\n\nHe hacks a console remotely.\n\nELARA\nNo more experiments!\n\nBut too late\u2014the void portal expands, sucking in echoes.\n\nLENA\nIt's collapsing! We have seconds!\n\nMARCUS\nGoodbye, crazy mes!\n\nThey board. The shuttle detaches as the station implodes.\n\nBut twist: As they escape, the void follows\u2014reality fractures ship-wide.\n\nSUPER CRAZY ENDING:\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:24:00]\nInside the shuttle: Everything merges. Elara becomes a pirate, Kai a dancing pineapple, Lena a robot, Marcus a tentacled alien\u2014all swapping bodies mid-sentence.\n\nPIRATE-ELARA (with eyepatch, arrr-ing)\nYarrr, set course for the quantum horizon!\n\nPINEAPPLE-KAI (bouncing)\nBut I'm fruity! This is bananas!\n\nROBOT-LENA (beeping)\nError: Logic overload. Dance protocol activated!\n\nThey all break into absurd dance as tentacles flail.\n\nALIEN-MARCUS\n(tentacles waving)\nIn my timeline, this is normal Tuesday!\n\nThe shuttle spins into the void\u2014screen fills with rainbow glitches, cartoon explosions, philosophical quotes scrolling like credits.\n\nVOICEOVER (overlapping echoes)\nInfinity... is... party time!\n\nThe ship vanishes into a black hole that burps confetti.\n\nFADE TO BLACK WITH A COMIC \"BOING\" SOUND.",
